halpha=\backslashdelta=\backslashgamma{\$}, this scenario is totally disfavored by the current SGL data, {\$}\backslashchi{\^{}}2{\_}{\{}\backslashrm min,\backslashgamma{\}} - \backslashchi{\^{}}2{\_}{\{}\backslashrm min,SIE{\}} \backslashsimeq 53{\$}.},
